<Author>kriskupn
<Content>Loved Pelayo! The hotel is in an excellent location, within walking distance to Las Ramblas, but far enough away from the maddening crowd. It is right around the corner from a ticket agency for day tours/bus tours. The lobby was small but the front desk clerk was friendly, answered questions, and was generally helpful. The room was large by European standards with a well appointed bathroom. There was also a t.v. and small refrigerator.I would definitely recommend the hotel for the price. By no means luxury but nice for the price! 
