<Author>reykjavik
<Content>Decent but a bit ghetto Its hard to explain this hotel. On one hand, the room was big, the staff was nice and they cleaned it well. On the other hand the ghetto entry way, staircase/elevator and all around hostel feel will leave you wondering why this is costing you a 100 bucks a night. But if youre used to having your dollar not go very far in Europe and you are not looking to stay at an elegant hotel then this place may be right for you.Conclusion: It was nice but no frills. If youre willing to spend a 100 a night on no frills, then definitely go for it. 
